This directory contains standalone files to run LBC_demo from the command line.

=================================
Generate the input meshes
=================================
LBC demo only supports pre-partitioned meshes. To generate the meshes:

  * Compile the planar_mesh_generator.
  * From lbc_demo/example:
    ../../../mesh_tools/bin/planar_mesh_generator mesh_config.nml

=================================
Run lbc_demo
=================================

  * Compile the lbc_demo program.
  * From lbc_demo/example:
    mpiexec -n 3 ../bin/lbc_demo configuration.nml

=================================
View the ouput
=================================
  * Can use the lfric tools ploterator
  * Note: The ploterator is under development and may not display all the fields.
    If there are issues, viewing a field, restart the ploterator and try again.
    (W2H_fields will not plot).

